text: Ole Gammelgaard Nielsen is an archer from Denmark. He was born on 20 November 1965. Nielsen competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics.Ole Gammelgaard NielsenOle Gammelgaard NIELSEN == References == Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Danish archers Category:Olympians for Denmark
